	<p>The tax aspects of the purchase, sale and merger of businesses are a vital part of the overall structure of the transaction. Our tax work is reflective of the Firm's sophisticated entities practice; that is, we work towards providing solutions for our clients that are creative, practical, and functional. </p>
<p>We provide advice on entity selection, as well as planning assistance for ongoing operations and specific transactions. </p>
<p>Additionally, our attorneys are often asked to provide opinion letters, which are commonly a condition to the consummation of a transaction.</p>
<h2>Tax-Exempt Entities</h2>
<p>Tax-exempt entities are also a part of our practice. We counsel organizations on their structure, formation, and operation to achieve and maintain tax-exempt status.</p>
